runtime_prompts.codegen_entity_list_json_schema:
Use this JSON schema exactly:
{
  "entities": [
    {"id": "string", "label": "string", "type": "string", "frequency": 0, "priority": 0}
  ]
}
Field rules:
- id: normalized snake_case identifier derived from label.
- label: exact surface form as it appears in causal data.
- type: one of ["actor", "resource", "environment", "policy"] — infer from context.
- frequency: integer count of occurrences across all causal data.
- priority: integer rank starting at 1; lower = generate first (most mentioned = 1).
